This directory currently contains no imported third-party SQLLogicTest corpus.

UltraSQL-authored helper files in this directory follow the workspace license:
Apache-2.0 OR MIT.

Before any external SQLLogicTest files are committed, copy the upstream license
or copyright notice into `third_party/sqllogictest/LICENSE.upstream`, record the
source commit in `third_party/sqllogictest/upstream_commit.txt`, and preserve
any per-file notices in the imported files.
